Package com.opengamma.strata.market.view Description

Package containing views of market data.

Each view interface provides a high-level view of a kind of market data, such as Ibor Index rates. The generic term "view" is used for the package, however individual types prefer to use more specific names, such as "discount factors" or "Ibor rates".
